{"key": "bubble_sort", "label": "Bubble Sort", "code": "def bubble_sort(arr):\n    n = len(arr)\n    for i in range(n):\n        for j in range(n - i - 1):\n            if arr[j] > arr[j + 1]:\n                arr[j], arr[j + 1] = arr[j + 1], arr[j]\n    return arr\n\n# Used by \"Analyze Big-O\": returns the args list for input size n\ndef gen_input(n):\n    return [list(range(n, 0, -1))]\n", "functionName": "bubble_sort", "argsText": "[[5, 2, 9, 1, 7]]", "timeline": [{"step": 0, "line_number": 2, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [5, 2, 9, 1, 7]}}, {"step": 1, "line_number": 3, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [5, 2, 9, 1, 7], "n": 5}}, {"step": 2, "line_number": 4, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [5, 2, 9, 1, 7], "n": 5, "i": 0}}, {"step": 3, "line_number": 5, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [5, 2, 9, 1, 7], "n": 5, "i": 0, "j": 0}}, {"step": 4, "line_number": 6, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [5, 2, 9, 1, 7], "n": 5, "i": 0, "j": 0}}, {"step": 5, "line_number": 4, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [2, 5, 9, 1, 7], "n": 5, "i": 0, "j": 0}}, {"step": 6, "line_number": 5, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [2, 5, 9, 1, 7], "n": 5, "i": 0, "j": 1}}, {"step": 7, "line_number": 4, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [2, 5, 9, 1, 7], "n": 5, "i": 0, "j": 1}}, {"step": 8, "line_number": 5, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [2, 5, 9, 1, 7], "n": 5, "i": 0, "j": 2}}, {"step": 9, "line_number": 6, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [2, 5, 9, 1, 7], "n": 5, "i": 0, "j": 2}}, {"step": 10, "line_number": 4, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [2, 5, 1, 9, 7], "n": 5, "i": 0, "j": 2}}, {"step": 11, "line_number": 5, "frame_name": "bubble_sort", "local_variables": {"arr": [2, 5, 1, 9, 7], "n": 5, "i": 0, "j": 3}}, {"step": 12, "line_number